social_posts.post_text: I think I just met the sweetest soul in the city. I had to stop this gentleman because I was so obsessed with his outfit and we ended up having such a lovely chat. He left me with an African Jasper crystal to make jewelry with but I left with so much more. Compliment someone’s outfit today! You might make a new friend, maybe get a little inspired even :)
